{"title":"天上银河　地上长江","authors":["梁上泉"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":9,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上银河　地上长江"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁上泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上有银河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地上有长江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银河呵不知宽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长江呵万里长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长长的流水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浩浩的波浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天辉映着太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜晚闪耀着星光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明星点点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么总在浪里波荡？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯标串串，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么竟有这般明亮？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因有位巨人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾在大江上漫步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"含笑踏着风波，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当作坦荡的平路。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指点挡道的礁阵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"礁阵撤退变通途；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指点两岸的支流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支流齐向主流倾注。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身后留下的脚印，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都化成了明星万颗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身后留下的脚印，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都化成了灯标无数。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯光星影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指出了行驶的航线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一直通向远处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通向远处……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远处，是深广的大海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引我们奔向未来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔向未来的道路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是惊涛澎湃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁甘作水底的泥沙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就只有被洪波淘汰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁想躲进避风的港湾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就只有无尽的等待，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"触不到时代的风云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进不到辽阔的世界。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时代的风云呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"应该握在我们的手掌；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辽阔的世界呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"应该装在我们的胸怀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心潮逐浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能负革命的重载；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激流奔涌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才会有浪花常开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪花常开开不败，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗争中青春永在！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上有银河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地上有长江。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长江——扬子江呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比那银河宽；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长江——扬子江呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比那银河长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这又宽又长的河床，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横贯中国，气势豪壮："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有前进的洪流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有倒退的波浪！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}